The back link reuses the same interface and parameters as the [Breadcrumbs](/components/Breadcrumb) component.
Always place back links before a page’s `<main>` content element.  This makes sure the [Skip to content](/components/skip-to-content) link allows the user to skip all navigation, including the back link.
Where possible this should be set in the [page template](/styles/page-template/) in `pageConfig`. This will ensure it will have the correct placing on the page.

