## When to use this component
Use the back link to help users go back to the previous page in a linear transaction, or the previous question in a questionnaire.  Use 'previous' as the label in a questionnaire when the previous page is a question.

## When not to use this component
Don’t use the back links component on websites with a flat structure.

If you’re using other navigational elements on the page, such as a sidebar, consider whether your users need the additional support of back links.

